早期投票类似于“无故缺席”投票。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Desilver|first1=Drew|last2=Geiger|first2=Abigail|title=For many Americans, Election Day is already here|url=http://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2016/10/21/for-many-americans-election-day-is-already-here/|website=www.pewresearch.org|publisher=Pew Research Center|accessdate=17 February 2017|archive-date=2017-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227182734/http://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2016/10/21/for-many-americans-election-day-is-already-here/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在许多美国州，早期投票期间在四至五十天不等。<ref>{{cite web|last1=White|first1=Daniel|title=These Are the States That Allow You to Vote Early|url=http://time.com/4495435/early-voting-states/|website=www.time.com|publisher=Time Magazine|accessdate=17 February 2017|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121155636/https://time.com/4495435/early-voting-states/|dead-url=no}}</ref>33个州和哥伦比亚特区，允许在没有任何理由情况下亲自参加早期投票，28个州和哥伦比亚特区允许无理由的通过邮寄方式参加早期投票。<ref name="ncsl-ae">[http://www.ncsl.org/legislatures-elections/elections/absentee-and-early-voting.aspx Absentee and Early Voting] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncsl.org/legislatures-elections/elections/absentee-and-early-voting.aspx |date=20131001190836 }}. [[National_Conference_of_State_Legislatures|National Conference of State Legislatures]].</ref>

